Dedication to the Game :

Switching between classes and coding sessions, or trying out other applications, isn't always easy.

For this example,
I'm offering a linear TI-89, this is a configuration, complete as possible to the factory settings, safer than manually via the Memory Menu.

You can easily remove useless settings & change every settîngs to your own.

I hope you'll find useful to insert `customkil()` or his code, somewhere between your own settings.
